<h1>Explore. What makes Guide Me different? </h1>
<p>What makes CityBuddy unique? The answer is easy...YOU! We all have unique ways in which we want to explore our world. Some peop;e like to hit up the tourist spots; others like to hang with the locals and get an inside feel of their destination. Some people like to do both. If you like a more intimate experience during your travels, you've come to the right place.</p>


<h2>Choose your tour guide</h2>
